trong></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left">\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style="color: #808080"><strong><span style="font-size: medium">经皮肤医学专家配方验证，无刺激，不过敏，不阻塞毛孔。</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left">\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style="color: #808080"><strong><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="color: #808080"><strong><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="color: #808080"><strong><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="color: #808080"><strong><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="color: #99ccff">规格</span>：35gNETWT.1.2OZ</span></strong></span></span></strong></span></span></strong></span>.</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left">\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style="color: #808080"><strong><span style="font-size: medium">*根据各地区域的不同防晒指数也有所变化</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left">\r\n	<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	<img alt="" src="http://tu.100xiu.net/huazhuangpin/0905/za057_01.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p align="center">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left">\r\n	<span style="color: #808080"><strong><span style="font-size: medium">产地：上海</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left">\r\n	<span style="color: #808080"><strong><span style="font-size: medium">请在标注日期前使用。</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left">\r\n	<span style="color: #808080"><strong><span style="font-size: medium">包装：纸盒包装</span></strong></span></p>\r\n', 55.80, NULL, NULL, 0.00, '', 6, 1, 'no', '2010-07-21 14:21:41', '2010-07-27 17:27:54', 'normal', 10, '144b875a014547f29c6bc7127952cfd3', '', '', 0),
('a54f535f50644ca88911453fe9c2e7a5', 'zh_CN', 'f55694efb5084c328bc109892be15bef', 'b08af48f708748e599e42e25ed6a710f', '资生堂 青春去皱眼霜20G 去黑眼圈/收紧眼周肌肤', '10', NULL, '青春去皱 去黑眼圈 收紧眼周肌肤', '2ce8473d07ff4cd8b7f3365723f3ec3b', '', '<p>\r\n	<font face="幼圆">&nbsp;<img alt="" src="/upload/201007/201007231522539175d21.jpg" style="width: 200px; height: 200px" /></font></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<font color="#cc0066" size="3">商品名称 Shiseido 资生堂青春<font face="Verdana">去皱</font>眼霜</font></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<font color="#cc0066" size="3">净含量 20g</font></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<font color="#cc0066" size="3">商品介绍</font></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<font color="#cc0066" size="3">含PAR-ELASTYL抗松驰成分及丰润抗皱配方，性质柔和直渗底层组织，为眼部肌肤补充水份，减轻干纹幼纹，促进血液循环，敷强眼周肌肤的弹性。而维他命A-E，可有效减退黑眼圈，收紧眼部周围肌肤，去除眼袋，令双眸焕发青春活力。</font></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<font color="#cc0066" face="Verdana" size="3">★★</font></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<font color="#cc0066" face="Verdana" size="3">此产品质地清澈如水，不油不腻。</font></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<font color="#cc0066" face="Verdana" size="3">含PAR-ELASTYL抗松驰成分及丰润抗皱配方，性质柔和直渗底层组织，为眼部肌肤补充水份，减轻干纹幼纹，促进血液循环，敷强眼周肌肤的弹性。而维他命A-E，可有效减退黑眼圈，收紧眼部周围肌肤，去除眼袋，令双眸焕发青春活力。<br />\r\n	【用法】<br />\r\n	压出适量于指尖，然后在眼周围加以按摩，方法是顺内眼角、上眼皮、眼尾、下眼皮做环形轻轻按摩，让肌肤完全吸收。每次眼霜的用量都不宜太多，眼部皮肤极薄，用得太多不但不能吸收，反而会给眼部肌肤造成负担加速衰老。正确的用量应是每次用两粒绿豆般大小即可。连续使用一周即可见效。</font></p>\r\n', 49.00, NULL, NULL, 0.00, '', 5, 1, 'no', '2010-07-21 13:57:39', '2010-07-27 17:28:17', 'normal', 10, '144b875a014547f29c6bc7127952cfd3', '', '', 0);
